        <h2>Dog Care</h2>
        <p>Here are some general instructions on how to care for a dog:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Feeding:</strong> Feed your dog a balanced diet appropriate for their age, size, and activity level.</li>
            <li><strong>Exercise:</strong> Provide regular exercise to keep your dog healthy and fit.</li>
            <li><strong>Grooming:</strong> Brush your dog's coat regularly and trim their nails as needed.</li>
            <li><strong>Training:</strong> Train your dog using positive reinforcement techniques to establish good behavior.</li>
            <li><strong>Veterinary Care:</strong> Schedule regular check-ups with your veterinarian and keep up with vaccinations and preventive care.</li>
            <li><strong>Socialization:</strong> Socialize your dog with other dogs and people to prevent behavioral issues.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For more detailed information, you can visit <a href="https://www.akc.org/dog-care/">American Kennel Club - Dog Care</a>.</p>
